                                <placeName ref="LOC3010Ethiop">Ethiopia</placeName>. They are used
                            as a point of reference to define the territories of groups such as the
                                <persName ref="ETH1223Basket">Basketo</persName>, the Dokko, the
                                <persName ref="ETH1188Balta">Balta</persName>, the <persName
                                ref="ETH1346Dafa">Dafa</persName>, the <persName ref="ETH1810Laha"
                                    >Laha</persName>, the Dola-Mašira, the Dime and the <persName ref="ETH1835Maale">Maale</persName>.</ab>
